Dear Sir,
I am working directly with a private investor from a Russia family who
is willing to provide project financing for credible clients with
feasible projects. The investor operates private owned funds and he is
ready and willing to consider big investment projects outside Russia
where they are currently heavily taxed by their opposition in
government. Currently, they have investment funds in the value above
500 Million United States Dollars available for investment projects.
The investor would be willing to consider a reliable and credible
individual or company to take up the opportunity to manage the funds
in investments as a proxy and in return generate Profits/Return on
Investment(ROI). The investor is interested to expand and explore
further business interest in banking, Financial Instruments, real
estate, mining,transportation,health sector, Food, oil and any sector
deemed feasible by the party.  We will be ready to discuss further
with a serious party.
Thank you.
Frank Williams
 fw2928319@gmail.com
